dct_title_s: Guatemala city graphic 1:12,500. Puerto Barrios and Puerto Santo Tomas de Castilla. Series E954
dct_description_sm: Map shows notable buildings, churches, hospitals, schools, powerlines, shorelines, quarries, roads, trails, tracks, bridges, populated areas, and woods. Includes inset guide to numbered features, index to streets, notes, glossary, and location maps. "Reprinted by NIMA 12-98." "Compiled in 1986 from best available sources." "NIMA Ref No. E954XPUERTOBARR." North Decimal Degree 15.744444 Alternate title: Puerto Barrios and Puerto Santo Tomas de Castilla. Transverse Mercator projection. "Reprinted by NIMA 12-98", "Compiled in 1986 from available sources". With a glossary. "Reprinted by NIMA 12-98". South Decimal Degree 15.675000 West Decimal Degree -88.627778 United States. National Imagery and Mapping Agency East Decimal Degree -88.566667
